ple for not helping you to solve your problems. The question is simple "are they the ones in the problem with you"? People may teach you, people may advise you, people may inspire you, but it takes YOU to go the extra mile and make an indelible impact!', 3301, 0), (209991, 'When you are able to know the right thing, you are intelligent. But when you choose that right thing to do, you are wise. This means people can get money, education, marriage, and good health and not get wisdom. Wisdom is the number one gift for a Godly success.', 3301, 0), (209992, 'Don''t settle for anything less. Rise up and optimize your talents through strategic thinking and big dream. Your God should be your guide in all things.', 3301, 0), (209993, 'Delay is not a help-mate. The cemetary is full of people who thought they could DO IT tomorrow. Do It Now!', 3301, 0), (209994, 'God is not interested in your ability. He isinterested in your availability. When you availyour ability to God, you become a faithful leader.', 3301, 0), (209995, 'You were saved not by work, but for work. Do it till all is done. By your Inventions, Innovations, Initiatives, Improvements, Involvements, Imaginations, Information, Interventions and Inspirations... Go the extra mile and dare to do it.', 3301, 0), (209996, 'Possessions and positions may promote our happiness but cannot create it. Happiness is a state created by self through the realization of how the self is important to the creator.', 3301, 0), (209997, 'God created everyone to love and to be loved; If you will not take care of people, just leave them as they came...DON''T SCRATCH THEM with your actions.', 3301, 0), (209998, 'We may propose many plans, let''s but remember that God can dispose our plans, propose a new and better ones and impose them on us!', 3301, 0), (209999, 'A “self-leader” is the positively influence you have on yourself and on others without any influence with your titles and positions. You must be able to lead yourself before you can lead others.', 3301, 0), (210000, 'Multiply your potentials with your plans and it will be equal to your purpose of existence. Your potentials are your seeds of greatness.', 3301, 0);
